query:
SELECT
            v2_job.workspace_id,
            COUNT(*)::BIGINT as "job_count!"
        FROM v2_job_completed
        JOIN v2_job ON v2_job.id = v2_job_completed.id
        WHERE v2_job.created_at >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '1 day'
        AND v2_job.created_at < CURRENT_DATE
        AND v2_job.workspace_id NOT LIKE 'wm-fork%'
        GROUP BY v2_job.workspace_id
